{"service_name": "Defining Control Requirements for Cloud Procurement Systems", "service_id": "7135048044797590", "company_name": "KPMG LLP", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     KPMG LLP\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Defining Control Requirements for Cloud Procurement Systems\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    KPMG\u2019s Cloud Risk and Control framework service addresses the challenges that public sector organisations have in managing risks to their key operational and financial processes. Delivery of this service through the Cloud can reduce the cost of risk and control procedures, improved / increased automation and delivery better business outcomes.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Business and process risk analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Control objective and risk management specification\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk and control framework development\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business process control optimisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Advice across the lifecycle of key systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Processes that support delivery of your services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enable automated approach to risk mitigation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Map where controls need improvement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High quality documentation, advice and experience\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Reduce the cost of risk and control procedures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enable automated and efficient risk mitigation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Be able to provide assurance to customers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Manage business risks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure suppliers understand risk requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Control risk around service delivery and financial performance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increased automation of risk controls and interlinked real-time operations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Build control specifications into procurement processes early\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Visibility over your service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Mitigate losses\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3250 per person\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93303/7135048044797590-pricing-document-2015-10-05-1755.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93303/7135048044797590-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-1755.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93303/713504804479759